def clas(st):
    coords = np.array([float(v) for v in str(st).split(' ')])[:3]
    temp = np.array([float(v) for v in str(st).split(' ')])[3:]
    if np.var(temp) > vthres:
        #temp = np.sqrt(temp)
        temp = temp - np.mean(temp)
        temp = temp/np.sqrt(np.var(temp))
        return model.predict(temp)
    else:
        return -1
